UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Ah, nothing quite like a ride on a gryphon, is there?  The night elves can keep those hippo\'s of theirs, just give me a gryphon and the wind in me hair!  $B$BWell now, I won\'t keep ye any longer, just head over to Gryth Thurden on the east side of The Great Forge and he\'ll get ye on yer way.', WHERE `entry`=2762;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Well now, ye\'ll need papers to form a guild, and Jondor Steelbrow can help you get started with the process. He can be found over at the Ironforge Visitor\'s Center when yer ready to get started.', WHERE `entry`=2764;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='' WHERE `entry`=2766;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Bah!  Mailboxes... all I get is junk mail lately!  $B$BIncrease the size of this... decrease the size of that... act now for your free Sword of Dragonslaying. I have to change my mailbox number every other month!  $B$BWell, ye can\'t say I didn\'t warn ye. If you\'re looking for the mailbox it\'s just outside the Stonefire Tavern.', WHERE `entry`=2769;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Do ye have the potential to be a skilled hunter?  Well $Gladdie : lassie;, only time will tell. Just don\'t ye go shooting at apples atop peoples\' heads till ye\'ve spoken with Regnus o\'er in the Hall of Arms.', WHERE `entry`=2770;
,`Text0_1_loc6`='That wee wizardly lass, Bink, over in the Hall of Mysteries would probably be able to help ye out with any magical needs you have.$B$BThe Hall of Mysteries is just north of the gates of Ironforge.'
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='That wee wizardly lass, Bink, over in the Hall of Mysteries would probably be able to help ye out with any magical needs you have.$B$BThe Hall of Mysteries is just north of the gates of Ironforge.', `Text1_0_loc6`='Well ye\'d be sure to find some training in the magical arts over in the Hall of Mysteries, north of the gates of Ironforge. Juli Stormkettle can always be found there with her nose in a book.', WHERE `entry`=2771;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Ah, nothing better than a priest to cure what ails ye. Of course a nice tall pint cures a lot of what ails ye too, but I don\'t think Braenna Flintcrag teaches brewing. I guess ye\'ll have to settle for some priest training over in the Hall of Mysteries instead.', WHERE `entry`=2772;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Ah, good ol\' Brandur Ironhammer. There\'s no doubt he\'ll provide ye with the guidance ye seek, $Glad : lass;. Ye\'ll find him in the Hall of Mysteries north of the gates of Ironforge.', WHERE `entry`=2773;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='All the roguish types hang out in The Forlorn Cavern, north of the gates of Ironforge. I\'d wager ye\'ll find Fenthwick there, no doubt counting the coin of another cut purse. I\'ll catch him one of these days!  $B$BIn the meantime I\'ll have my eye on you as well, $Glad : lass;.', WHERE `entry`=2774;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='A warlock, eh... Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $Gboyo : girlie;. I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them. Ye get me?  $B$BNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern. That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart.', WHERE `entry`=2775;

UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $B$BI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to. I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.', WHERE `entry`=2776;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='' WHERE `entry`=2793;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Yer looking for an Alchemy trainer are ye?  Just came from there, I did. Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather. $B$B::sigh:: ...why o\' why didn\'t I take the blue potion.', WHERE `entry`=2794;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.', WHERE `entry`=2795;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook. Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.', WHERE `entry`=2796;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $Glad : lass;. I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy. $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble. He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.', WHERE `entry`=2797;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then. Why that little gnome and his gadgets... Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?', WHERE `entry`=2798;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me. If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from. Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician.', WHERE `entry`=2799;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword. Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which. Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was.', WHERE `entry`=2800;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Oh, ye want to learn to pick some daisies do ye?  Ha!  I\'m just teasing ye $Gladdie : lass;. $B$BA fine profession it is, and Reyna Stonebranch can show ye how it\'s done. She works at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge.', WHERE `entry`=2801;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Sure ye don\'t want to be a Blacksmith?  Well, if yer heart is set on Leatherworking, then you best talk to Fimble Finespindle over at his shop on the northwest side of The Great Forge.', WHERE `entry`=2802;
,`Text1_0_loc6`='Well well!  You\'ve come to the right place to learn Mining, $Gboyo : girlie;!  Geofram Bouldertoe himself resides at the Deepmountain Mining Guild. Ye couldn\'t ask for a better instructor than him.'
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Skinning?  The only thing ye look like ye could skin is yer own knee!  Ha!  Now why don\'t you go see Balthus Stoneflayer so he can teach you how to properly skin some animals. You\'ll find him in Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.', WHERE `entry`=2805;
UPDATE `locales_npc_text` SET `Text0_1_loc6`='', `Text1_0_loc6`='Ye might not know it, but in addition to being a skilled tailor, Jormund is also a slayer of giants!  Why he must have overheard a few of us sharing stories when he shouted that he\'d killed seven with one blow!  $B$BYe should pay him a visit at his store on the north side of The Great Forge an\' see if he\'ll tell ye the tale!', WHERE `entry`=2807;
